Tue Apr 24 10:54:34 2012  NAKAMURA Usaku  <usa@ruby-lang.org>

	* test/drb/drbtest.rb ({DRbCore,DRbAry}#teardown): cannot pass SIGTERM
	  to another process on Windows, so use SIGINT instead.

